sms.body:
Greetings,
My name is Stella from IAT(Institute of Advanced Technology)
This is to notify you that we are starting registrations for JAVA Class from 23rd May 2022 from 8:30AM - 11:30AM EVENING CLASSES 5:30PM - 8:30PM
It is a Eight weeks course.
After this program you will be able to understand:
- Compile and run a Java Application. - Understand the role of the JAVA Virtual Machine in achieving platform independence. - Navigate through the API docs - Use the Object Oriented Paradigm in JAVA Programs. - Understand the division of classes into JAVA Packages. - Use Exception to handle run time errors. - Select the proper I/O class among those provided by the JDK. - Use thread in order to create more efficient JAVA Programs.
C# - Inheritance and Polymorphism. - Boolean Logic - Loops and Arrays - interfaces and Abstract Classes in C#. - Debugging and Enums. - Generic Types. - Threading
To register or know more about this course, Call/Text/WhatsApp 0719736389 .
Kind Regards, Career Advisor, IAT Pension Towers.
